'''Agarsafen''' (Iguersafène), (s [[tifinaɣ]] : ''ⴰⴳⴰⵔⵙⴰⴼⴻⵏ'' , s tefṛansist : Iguersafène, s taɛṛabt : اقرسافن) tezga-d deg-wemalu n wekfadu, di tɣiwant n [[Ta ɣiwant n At Yeǧǧer|At Yeǧǧaṛ]] id yezgan deg-wusamar n [[Tizi Wezzu]] ; Deg-wakal-is id tella tɣiwant. Tebɛed azal n 70 ikilumiṭṛen ɣaf temdint n [[Tizi Wezzu]].

.Aɛlayet ɣaf lebḥaṛ azal n 890  lmitrat.

.Γuṛes ugar n 4 000 imezdaɣ.
